snippet.textDisplay:
My definition of the video:
Alex is in a therapy session with all these different “people” which are actually different parts of him (that is the disaster mix-liar, cynic, sinner, saint..) where they all learn to cooperate with each other and he learns how to accept them as a part of himself. The message is that we all have parts of ourselves that we like or dislike, but to function better we have to learn how to communicate and understand each part and accept that that is who we are while learning how to love ourselves, be it by going to therapy or having friends around or simply going through the process alone.

The rest of the guys being there might have some kind of meaning (like being there and showing support for Alex) or they could be there because they are a part of the band and it makes no sense to make a music video with just Alex in it..
That’s all folks!
